ported average monetizable daily active users. If 5% of those mDAUs are bot=
s, then Twitter makes something like $5.52 per (non-bot) user per quarter. =
But if 25% of the users are bots, then Twitter makes something like $6.99 p=
er user per quarter: Each real Twitter user generates more revenue than you=
