, and thus for its valuation.Now, this is not a complete=C2=A0analysis: If =
Twitter=C2=A0has=C2=A0been lying about its users to advertisers, the advert=
isers will be mad, and that probably won=E2=80=99t be good for future reven=
ue. And of course all of this is dumb because there is no evidence at all t=
