ice of the in-game tokens has crashed, then the play-to-earn part doesn=E2=
=80=99t really work does it? What you are left with is just paying a lot of=
 money to play a video game. Which people do all the time! There is a whole=
 giant video-game industry that makes fun games and sells them to people fo=
r money!=C2=A0But that=E2=80=99s apparently=C2=A0not why people played=C2=
=A0Axie.
